==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Assibilation
<hw>As*sib`i*la"tion</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Change of a non-sibilant
letter to a sibilant, as of -<xex>tion</xex> to -<xex>shun</xex>,
<xex>duke</xex> to <xex>ditch</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Assidean</ent>⟦br⟧
